Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是黑巫女  椿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是前来阻挠咒术的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒老早就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的  我是来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难伺候的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们想借用一下那股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还很痛恨桔梗对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第60话 黑巫女 五十年的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个你念念看  日暮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前学过的也忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像愈来愈被抛在后面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是那个  旧男友的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个明明劈腿甩掉戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又爱吃醋的暴力任性男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是还牵扯不清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神嘛  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点忘了他比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛  那个臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他果然不想分手对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要干脆点分了才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…那个呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又回到原点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个男的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他也有温柔的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很平常嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么这么沮丧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我最近一直请假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课业有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  因为戈薇常常请假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算每天上课也有可能跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是只要确实做好预习与复习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上课就能很快乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么怎么怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了不好的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为步美一直很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是太晚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙又会跑来接我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还会来接你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真的是很体贴的男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  他明明很爱吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且很任性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们又和好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇这样没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是致密的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧了  老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑巫女  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我来到底有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约五十年前  你应该还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾和叫做桔梗的巫女战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了夺取四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的真清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑巫女  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那邪恶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意为我所用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借给你力量  我能得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就给你四魂之玉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你的手上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆变的妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意你的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我本来的面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个女人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了永保青春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把魂魄出卖给妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且对方还是不怎样的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人应该渴望更强的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你说有四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算用四魂之玉做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是永保青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你希望我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给七宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是犬夜叉喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别只顾着拿零嘴…拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样的也该带一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多各式各样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御神酒和护身符也带去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不用了啦  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你已经要出发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有人在等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是犬夜叉哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想试着去战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你去了  因为你是胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就会想回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太年纪还太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐就不会怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概都已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就放着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有够久耶  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说太阳下山前就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说太阳下山前就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有感觉到什么吧  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有股奇怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是法师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…邪气悄悄的接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛在地面上爬一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?被咬了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  很慢耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道被什么东西咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纸?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到那女人的血了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  再带我过去一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很神气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我碰到一个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该算是解决掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没有被咬的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确有个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看那纸  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有带来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…式神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,式神?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚是…四魂之玉碎片?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片变黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片  进入了我的身体里?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入那女人体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会和充满奈落污秽的玉共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而侵蚀那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是心灵还是身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人的命运就任我摆布了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿  别小看那个叫戈薇的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫戈薇的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己中了诅咒都没发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为桔梗的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个多厉害的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你想怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样直接咒杀她也行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让犬夜叉的恶梦再次重现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那与心爱的女人相互残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人怀念的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫姥姥  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上之前的邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是某人在诅咒戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁敢诅咒戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是黑巫女的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在井边咬伤戈薇的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是黑巫女的使魔  式神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:15:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑巫女?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该也知道她们的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专门接受诅咒委托的邪恶巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片受到污染
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是那家伙的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全进入戈薇的身体里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇或许会被碎片的毒毒死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出黑巫女然后打倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要断绝诅咒非这样做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你留下来陪在戈薇身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样比较妥当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这个方向可以感受到邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上来  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了犬夜叉  杀了犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…别说了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还任性的抵抗着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了  椿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫戈薇的女人\N是巫女桔梗的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的手段是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一个半妖男人夺去了心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵力也衰弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取那家伙守护的四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这原本是最好的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人竟然把我放的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原封不动的打回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滚  我不想取你性命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人故作清高的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来仍让我作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我去换个水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇还有救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…可能戈薇本身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在和诅咒战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇是很坚强的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  再拖下去会承受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还束手无策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她垂死挣扎也差不多到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就实现你的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒他们还没\N抵达黑巫女的所在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇明明这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然只能旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧  犬夜叉!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使身体被操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的心却还没丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这样更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿  如果犬夜叉逃离那地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就不用客气  咒杀戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇一定是被黑巫女操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪气愈来愈强了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经和它战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人我随时都能咒杀她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:22:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样让戈薇杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是逃走  让戈薇丧命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量痛苦吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:24.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
